<topic id='business_definition_drug_misuse_episode.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Drug Misuse Episode (Retired) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
               keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_episode">Drug Misuse Episode</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_group">ACTIVITY GROUP</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
               keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_episode">Drug Misuse Episode</xref>
 is an episode of care provided to a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
               keyref="business_definition_drug_misuser">Drug Misuser</xref>.        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_episode">Drug Misuse Episode</xref>
 starts when a 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuser">Drug Misuser</xref>
 is triaged by a 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_agency">Drug Misuse Agency</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_episode">Drug Misuse Episode</xref>
 ends when a 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuser">Drug Misuser</xref>
 is discharged from the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuse_episode">Drug Misuse Episode</xref>
 or when the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuser">Drug Misuser</xref>
 has not been seen or received treatment for a default period of 2 months with the likelihood that the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition retired"
                        keyref="business_definition_drug_misuser">Drug Misuser</xref>
 will continue with the treatment.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
